# Cloudflare Workers static-assets redirects.
#
# SPA routing (every unmatched path → app shell) is handled by wrangler.jsonc
# `assets.not_found_handling = "single-page-application"`. Do NOT add a
# `/*  /index.html  200` rule here — Workers static assets rejects it as an
# infinite-loop redirect.
#
# The www → apex canonical redirect cannot live here either: Workers static
# assets `_redirects` only allows relative URLs, not absolute ones with a host.
# When a custom domain is attached, configure www → apex as a Cloudflare
# Redirect Rule / Bulk Redirect in the dashboard instead.
